  <summary date="2021-06-21T15:24:22Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Food Supply Protection Act of 2020

This bill provides assistance to food organizations to protect the continuity of the food supply chain during the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) public health emergency, including by providing grants that support the purchase or distribution of surplus perishable food or meals prepared with such food.</summary>
